description: This file defines a data model for movie scripts using Pydantic, and sets up two Agent instances for generating movie scripts via OpenAI's GPT-4 model, one using JSON mode and the other using structured output.

classes.name: MovieScript
classes.description: A Pydantic model representing the structure of a movie script, including setting, ending, genre, name, characters, storyline, and rating.

methods.name: print_response
methods.description: Method called on both agents to print the response for a given prompt.
